2023-11-01 00:35:35.311 EDT [ 99352 4/3066 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  statement: COMMIT
2023-11-01 00:35:35.311 EDT [ 99352 4/0 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  duration: 0.045 ms
