2023-11-01 00:50:39.956 EDT [ 99353 4/3170 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  duration: 28.902 ms
2023-11-01 00:50:39.957 EDT [ 99353 4/3170 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  statement: COMMIT
2023-11-01 00:50:39.957 EDT [ 99353 4/0 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  duration: 0.049 ms
